<Class name="CM_BulkRelease" id="48efe2d2-9922-49ff-ae84-1cb5215c74ad">
    <superclass name="CM_Object"/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>TH2:
Maintains information relating to any sort of cargo activity request.

(the presence of the word 'bulk' is somewhat missleading, actually so is
the word 'release': Instances of this class represent any kind request 
for something to happen to some cargo. Normally this will be releasing it from the 
terminal, but at this time (2007) can also include packing)</text>
    <DbClassMap file="operatn"/>
