    <JadeMethod name="isTrackedItemAssigned" id="b37699bd-89b1-454d-9a8d-a96900664aa3">
        <source>isTrackedItemAssigned(_ti : CM_TrackedItem) : Boolean;
/*
Purpose:			Returns true if ti in allTrackedItemsAssigned	
Parameters:			_ti - Tracked Item to check
Return Value:		true if ti exists in allTrackedItemsAssigned

Date		Who		Reason
14 December 2010	cnwmh5	Initial creation #26586
